description: Try our easy to follow Orange & Poppy Seed Cake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Orange & Poppy Seed Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Beat sifted icing sugar, 30g soft butter, and cream cheese together until smooth to create the frosting. Add 1 tbs of orange juice and mix until frosting is creamy. Spread over cooled cake. Cut into slices to serve.
